Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.57,0:00:28.78,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,一二三
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.28,0:00:33.08,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,不死樹
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.12,0:00:35.58,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,何為真相
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.83,0:00:39.54,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,我將成為真相
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.09,0:00:50.51,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,我看到那片光亮
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.47,0:00:56.85,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,這就是我的全部
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.56,0:00:59.31,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,你說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.52,0:01:01.40,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.02,0:01:05.99,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,你為什麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.20,0:01:11.49,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,磨刀 小憩
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.49,0:01:14.70,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,生存之景
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.70,0:01:18.33,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,詩和快樂是未來
